  <brief_title>Efficacy/Safety of Pseudoephedrine Plus Levocetirizine Versus Placebo in Patients With Vasomotor Rhinitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of Cossac L Tablet in Vasomotor Rhinitis Patients : A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Phase 3 Clinical Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
