  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate efficacy and safety of Cossac L tablet in the
      treatment of vasomotor rhinitis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled, phase 3
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
